txt.en: Evil-looking flies can be found in plenty around the Black Heart. These creatures would devour you in a heart beat, if allowed.\n\nYou should defeat some of them.
You have rid the forest of many a harrying, evil insect. This act was a kindness to all inhabitants of Fangorn.
